'''美德樂'''（Medela）是一家[[瑞士|瑞士]]的醫療器材商，其核心事業為[[哺乳|哺乳]]器材[[研發|研發]]及[[製造|製造]]。研究已經深深植入 Medela（美德樂） 的DNA 之中。許多其他公司只是把“研究”作為宣傳噱頭，而 Medela（美德樂） 擁有長期的基礎研究和探索性研究背景，因此能在業內脫穎而出。三十多年來，公司堅持以“研究”作為其核心價值以及各項活動的重中之重。<ref name=mirror>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/medela-issues-recall-three-breast-8929967|title=Medela issues recall on three breast pump ranges amid safety concerns|last=Oakley|first=Nicola|date=2016-09-28|newspaper=mirror|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211083206/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/medela-issues-recall-three-breast-8929967|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.drugstorenews.com/article/medela-launches-state-art-breast-pump|title=Medela launches state-of-the-art breast pump|accessdate=2017-02-10|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211082757/http://www.drugstorenews.com/article/medela-launches-state-art-breast-pump|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.which.co.uk/news/2016/10/safety-warning-on-medela-breast-pumps-453693/|title=Safety warning on Medela breast pumps - October - 2016 - Which? News|accessdate=2017-02-10|work=www.which.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210120906/http://www.which.co.uk/news/2016/10/safety-warning-on-medela-breast-pumps-453693/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
1961年，Olle Larsson在瑞士[[楚格|楚格]]創立美德樂公司；後來，美德樂在Larsson家族的持有下逐漸成長。

2016年年底，美德樂正式公開其研發之無線控制集乳器。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://now.howstuffworks.com/2017/01/13/breast-best-when-wireless|title=Now - HowStuffWorks|accessdate=2017-02-10|work=now.howstuffworks.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210114437/http://now.howstuffworks.com/2017/01/13/breast-best-when-wireless|archive-date=2017-02-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/medela-introduces-first-smart-breast-pump-designed-with-moms-in-mind-300369680.html|title=Medela Introduces First Smart Breast Pump Designed with Moms in Mind|accessdate=2017-02-10|last=Inc.|first=Medela,|work=www.prnewswire.com|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210114503/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/medela-introduces-first-smart-breast-pump-designed-with-moms-in-mind-300369680.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nwherald.com/2017/01/05/medela-launches-sonata-pump/aqo2l2q/|title=Medela launches Sonata pump|accessdate=2017-02-10|last=Newswire|first=P. R.|work=Northwest Herald|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210120609/http://www.nwherald.com/2017/01/05/medela-launches-sonata-pump/aqo2l2q/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 全球事業 ==
美德樂藉其旗下18家子公司經銷及服務於超過90個國家及地區。1980年代末期，美德樂在美國成立子公司Medela, Inc.，並持續服務美國境內市場至今。


